<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1556,2030]" box="[151,1118,1556,1579]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,290,1556,1579]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Description.</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[296,412,1556,1579]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Body color</emphasis>
. Background yellow to brown with dark brown irrorate markings.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1556,2030]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis box="[199,329,1591,1614]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Morphology</emphasis>
. Head distinctly narrower than pronotum, discal portion of crown glabrous; slightly produced in dorsal view; crown midlength longer than next to eyes; anterior margin of head with two transverse striations. Pronotum not exceeding eyes anteriorly, lateral margin carinate, lateral margin longer than basal width of eye. Lorum wider than clypellus near base. Antennal base near middle of eye; antennal ledge weakly carinate. Clypellus widening apically. Ocelli present, close to eyes, on anterior margin of head.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1556,2030]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Forewing with four apical cells and three subapical cells, inner subapical cell open (second m-cu crossvein absent) and outer one short, without crossvein between claval veins (
<figureCitation box="[801,866,1799,1822]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 5" captionStartId="1.[151,258,997,1019]" captionTargetBox="[191,1386,202,963]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[188,1398,194,974]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 5. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 1. ♂, dorsal view; 2. ♂, lateral view; 3. ♂, face; 4. ♂, head in anterior view; 5. Forewing." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259705/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[851,866,1799,1822]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="5.0">5</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1556,2030]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis box="[199,355,1834,1857]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Male genitalia</emphasis>
. Pygofer lobes narrowly rounded posteriorly; with macrosetae; without processes (
<figureCitation box="[1237,1302,1834,1857]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[1286,1302,1834,1857]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="6.0">6</number>
</figureCitation>
). Valve very short (
<figureCitation box="[218,282,1869,1892]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[267,282,1869,1892]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
). Subgenital plate apices narrow, elongate; few short fine setae at subbase laterally; without macrosetae (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[151,166,1903,1926]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
). Style broad at base, abruptly narrowing subapically, preapical lobe with fine setae, apex short (
<figureCitation box="[1197,1262,1903,1926]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[1247,1262,1903,1926]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
). Connective Yshaped; broad and short (
<figureCitation box="[426,506,1938,1961]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Fig. 
<number box="[478,506,1938,1961]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="11.0">11</number>
</figureCitation>
). Aedeagus laterally compressed; with one pair of ventral processes; gonopore apical (
<figureCitation box="[158,269,1973,1996]" captionStart="FIGURES 6 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1537,1559]" captionTargetBox="[150,1436,191,1505]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[150,1436,191,1515]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 6 – 12. Brevivalvala melanosticta sp. nov. 6. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 8. Style, dorsal view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Profemur and protibial, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/259706/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Figs 
<number box="[212,269,1973,1996]" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" value="9.1">9, 10</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
