<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="82" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1086,1282]" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,327,1224,1247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new genus name is derived from the Latin word “ 
<emphasis box="[911,977,1224,1247]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">Brevi-</emphasis>
” (short) and “ 
<emphasis box="[1130,1208,1224,1247]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">valvala</emphasis>
” (valve), referring to the short valve.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
